# XCTest Assertions

Use specific assertion methods instead of boolean comparisons:

```swift
// ❌ BAD
XCTAssertTrue(a == b)
XCTAssertFalse(a == b)
XCTAssertTrue(a === b)

// ✅ GOOD
XCTAssertEqual(a, b)
XCTAssertNotEqual(a, b)
XCTAssertIdentical(a, b)
```

Specific assertions provide better failure messages showing actual vs expected values.
